summary: An email from June 20, 2019, discussing an analysis of Jeffrey Epstein's flight manifest records to identify individuals who traveled with him within the previous year. The email lists nine entries, but all identifying details (names and dates of birth) are redacted.

events.title: Analysis of Epstein's Flight Manifests
events.description: An individual reviewed Jeffrey Epstein's flight manifest records to identify people who traveled with him within the last year, resulting in a list of nine individuals.

keyFacts: An email from June 20, 2019, discusses an analysis of Jeffrey Epstein's flight manifest records.
The analysis identified nine individuals who traveled with Epstein within the year prior to June 2019.
All identifying information for the nine individuals (names and dates of birth) is completely redacted in the provided text.
